reviews.text: A little friendly and cosy restaurant. Waiters are polite and helpful. Food selections are different from major chain store restaurants and with good decor. The price is a bit above average, but the food are good. The waffle is excellent.
The seasoning on the food is great.  Seafood seems fresh as well.  The setting overall is comfy with comfortable interior design.  Not to mention it's literally just opposite the mtr station
Prawns not properly defrosted. Grey colored. Cold food colder service.

Reasonable priced food, but service was poor, both the waiter and waitress seemed to fail to understand simple ways to serve.
Soup & the main course was served before my partner arrived. When they served the soup, i told them to wait until my partner arrives before serving the main, but they didnt take any notice.
Good food and drinks and staffs but some noisy people sitting around

result.adr_address: 香港上環永樂街50號
result.name: La Postre

reviews.text:
上到黎見到隻碟同餐具感覺似曾相識，再望下本餐牌，原來我已經去過尖沙咀厚福街的分店，可想而知餐廳設計的統一性多重要！

整體服務態度十分好，讓他們來回添了多回水他們的表情、語氣沒有不耐煩，上菜速度亦整體亦十分快。

一打開餐牌，其食品放置的版面設計一定有深思熟慮，否則怎麼會甜品放在前呢？第一下已經被窩夫吸引了！

以下跟據個人喜愛程度排序：
抹茶麻糬窩夫：除了雪糕在窩夫上外，紅豆蓉、糖漿、抹茶醬、吉士醬都是分開的，
因此我們可以自行DIY，分配理想的份量 最後還剩餘糖漿、抹茶醬跟吉士醬！窩夫即叫即製，上臺時還是暖呼呼，烘得外脆內軟，還貼心的切好四份，配上雪糕及紅豆蓉，甜度已經剛剛好！

西班牙海鮮飯：OpenRice 網上預訂優惠減$100，所以必點！🤣 雖然要了少辣，完全不受辣的友人還是感覺辣。飯粒煙韌乾身、蝦可能過熟略嫌不夠彈牙。

無花果墨魚沙律：正正常常吧，沙律菜新鮮清甜，喜歡新鮮無花果及醋汁，唯墨魚沒有驚喜。

芝士煎蟹餅：睇相及賣相相當吸引，芝士、菇加蛋這個組合絕對飽肚，原以為內有蟹肉，可是所謂的蟹只是6隻小蟹鉗，而且蛋餅煎得過為乾身，不夠嫩滑，稍為失色。

A little friendly and cosy restaurant. Waiters are polite and helpful. Food selections are different from major chain store restaurants and with good decor. The price is a bit above average, but the food are good. The waffle is excellent.
The seasoning on the food is great.  Seafood seems fresh as well.  The setting overall is comfy with comfortable interior design.  Not to mention it's literally just opposite the mtr station
Prawns not properly defrosted. Grey colored. Cold food colder service.

Reasonable priced food, but service was poor, both the waiter and waitress seemed to fail to understand simple ways to serve.
Soup & the main course was served before my partner arrived. When they served the soup, i told them to wait until my partner arrives before serving the main, but they didnt take any notice.
